Usage: get_ccopt_clock_tree_capacitance [-help] <instTerm|term>
                                        [-edge {rise fall both}] [ -delay_corner <delay_corner> ] [ -load | -wire ] [ -delay_type <type> ]

-help                            # Prints out the command usage
<instTerm|term>                  # pin to query capacitance for
                                 # ((instTerm|term), required)
-delay_corner <delay_corner>     # for this delay corner
                                 # ((delay_corner), optional)
-delay_type {early late}         # for this delay type (enum, optional)
-edge {rise fall both}           # for this edge (enum, optional)
-load                            # only return the driven load capacitance
                                 # (bool, optional)
-wire                            # only return the driven wire capacitance
                                 # (bool, optional)